    "Details": "Introduced during the FedCom Civil War, the 1C's replaces the LB-X AC/5 with an RAC/5. Two tons of CASE protected ammunition is carried to feed the hungry weapon; when this is depleted the left torso mounted ER medium laser is the 'Mech's only fallback weapon.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Extended Torso Twist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
